
What is http?
Http is a protocol also known as the foundation of data communication which means it transfer the data on www.
It helps in transmission of data from client end to server end.

-----------------
What are safe methods?
Methods like    HEAD , GET , OPTIONS , TRACE are called as   safe methods because they are only intended to get the information from the servcer and are not meant to change the state of the origin server.


-------------------


Before http 1.0 connection were terminated after one request response pair but after 1.0 connection are kept alive so it can be used for more than one requests -> thats called persistant connections in http